---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="会社概要 | 株式会社Bridge">
  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">会社概要</h1>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p><span class="font-medium">会社名</span>：株式会社Bridge</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">所在地</span>：東京都（仮）</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">代表者</span>：代表取締役（仮）</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">設立</span>：YYYY年MM月（仮）</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p><span class="font-medium">事業内容</span>：不動産売買・仲介・投資 等</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">電話番号</span>：00-0000-0000（仮）</p>
          <p><span class="font-medium">メール</span>：info@example.com（仮）</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

